<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mn ywm mạ ʿrfth</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- mn ywm mạ ʿrfth wmlạny bslạm wạ̉frạḥ
 wyạ ạ̉gẖạny
 ṭmn qlby ʿly̱ ạ̉yạmy ạ̹nh mʿạya ṭwl ạlmsẖwạr
 1- dạ str kl ʿywb wgẖfr ly dẖnwby
 kẖd ḥkmy wạ̹dạny kẖlạṣ mjạny
 wqạl ly ạmḍi bslạm
 2- mn bʿd ạlạ̉ḥzạn kẖlạny frḥạn
 whmwmy ạnzạḥt wḥyạty ạrtạḥt
 sẖạl ʿny kl ạlạ̉ḥmạl
 3- dạ rfʿny bạ̹ydyh fwq ʿly̱ mnkbyh
 ạlrb rạʿy wmsyj ḥwạly</lyrics>
